1
00:00:08,274 --> 00:00:09,376
Why'd you lock the door?

2
00:00:15,448 --> 00:00:16,448
Hey, what are you doing?

3
00:00:38,471 --> 00:00:39,471
Wait a second.

4
00:00:40,073 --> 00:00:41,407
We're in the dressing room.

5
00:00:41,408 --> 00:00:42,442
People are right outside.

6
00:00:49,983 --> 00:00:51,103
Quite the flirt, aren't you?

7
00:01:11,438 --> 00:01:12,505
Ow, that hurts!

8
00:01:13,239 --> 00:01:14,307
Stop poking me.

9
00:01:15,275 --> 00:01:16,409
I did not!

10
00:01:17,877 --> 00:01:18,877
It tickles right here.

11
00:01:19,946 --> 00:01:21,380
You kept tickling me on stage.

12
00:01:21,381 --> 00:01:22,481
No, I was just reminding you

13
00:01:22,482 --> 00:01:23,817
to get into position.

14
00:01:29,255 --> 00:01:30,924
And all that whispering...

15
00:01:34,194 --> 00:01:35,595
Don't you dare do that again.

16
00:01:54,614 --> 00:01:56,149
You hear me?

17
00:02:05,325 --> 00:02:06,793
Fine. Now get changed.
